2019-03-17T13:44:50.000Z","msg":"或是調轉諗 係政府唔滿意呢家大陽春（政府管治威望下降，調控樓市再失敗）搵佢做喉舌 等d地產商唔好太串<br />\n<br />\nPs 9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2636ba85d6bc445afff482d8553fdee166ec58a","tid":1065333,"uid":771,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"其實年年通漲3-4%+ 有樓既人本身就係搵到錢果班<br />\n係供應唔係大增既情況下，樓價只會gogogo<br />\n<br />\n幾個情況下一齊出現會跌<br />\n1. 政府重稅，基本上買樓唔會再有資本增值<br />\n2. 供應大增<br />\n3. 經濟差到出現大量斷供<br />\n<br />\n但出現跌市時一定連冇樓既市民都一齊食屎<br />\n所以窮人等食屎啦，升跌都係食屎"},{"pid":"34938e6fa8598fa9fc42cd60e4464eb3fb758bee","tid":1065333,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"黃遠輝做房策，如果佢話樓價將來唔會跌咪即係話佢做唔到野😂"},{"pid":"8ee32b1b7857c603e1a2abdc0269ee9f6642a9bb","tid":1065333,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b633b7eb6c2bbd5431e542d62ef69821aedf2619","tid":1065333,"uid":81113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Mark my word: 條友講緊真話</span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎Binc"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"而家咁嘅勢就算真係跌一成都係高過11月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f8d398c320828b74a86f88e59f98f1dda4d17b","tid":1065333,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34938e6fa8598fa9fc42cd60e4464eb3fb758bee","tid":1065333,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"黃遠輝做房策，如果佢話樓價將來唔會跌咪即係話佢做唔到野😂"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"佢有西權力咩，林鄭棄將，同周永新一鳩樣，廢淡出去睇下樓同抽新樓，睇下有無得跌"},{"pid":"b1bb8b4df26202239e9223d13698b8790f76ad2a","tid":1065333,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51f8d398c320828b74a86f88e59f98f1dda4d17b","tid":1065333,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34938e6fa8598fa9fc42cd60e4464eb3fb758bee","tid":1065333,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score